Baby Cele - Maloka (amụrụ n' abali iri abụọ Na abụọ nke ọnwa Maachi afọ 1972)  bụ onye South Africa na-eme ihe nkiri a mụrụ na Umlazi, KwaZulu-Natal

Cele nwetara nkwanye ùgwù maka ọrụ ya dị ka Kaltego Rathebe, onye ọ gosipụtara ruo afọ asatọ na ihe nkiri telivishọnke nke na-adigizi nke ndị ntorobịa e.tv Backstage. Ọ gara n'ihu na-arụ ọrụ n' ọnọdụ Portia na SABC 1 sitcom My Perfect Family
N'afọ 2011, ọ gosipụtara ọrụ nke Beauty na obere usoro Shreds & Dreams, dabere na egwuregwu 2004 nke Clare Stopford.
Site n'afọ 2012 ruo afọ 2013, o gosipụtara àgwà Slindile Dludlu na Mzansi Magic telenovela Inkaba

Cele gosikwara dị ka Gasta Cele na ihe nkiri Zabalaza
N'afọ 2016, o gosipụtara àgwà Sibongile Nene na Isidingo
Ọ bụkwa onye otu egwu Sarafina!
Cele gosipụtakwara agwa ya n' ihe nkiri na egwuregwu Cards.
N'afọ 2018, ọ sonyeere ndị otu telenovela Uzalo, ebe ọ na-egosi àgwà Gabisile Mdletshe
Cele lụrụ onye Oji ego achụ ego Thabo Maloka. Ọ bụ nne nke ụmụ abụọ.
